---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Meet Brendan McAdams — B2B sales coach and consultant helping health tech companies build predictable revenue."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h1>About Brendan</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="lead">I've spent my career at the intersection of health technology and B2B sales — helping companies turn promising products into predictable revenue engines.</p>

        <h2>Why I Do This</h2>
        <p>Health tech founders build incredible products. They solve real problems for hospitals, clinics, insurers, and patients. But too many of them struggle to sell — not because their product isn't good, but because nobody taught them how B2B sales actually works in healthcare.</p>
        <p>I bridge that gap. I take the complexity out of enterprise sales and give founders and sales teams a clear, repeatable process to win deals and grow revenue.</p>

        <h2>What I Bring</h2>
        <p>Deep experience selling into health systems, payers, and life sciences companies. I've seen what works and what doesn't across hundreds of sales cycles. I know the objections before they come up. I know when a deal is real and when it's just a polite "maybe."</p>
        <p>My approach is direct, practical, and built for people who don't have time for theory. We work on your actual deals, your actual calls, your actual pipeline.</p>

        <h2>The Name</h2>
        <p><strong>Create Revenue</strong> is exactly what we do together. Not "hope for revenue" or "discuss revenue strategy in a workshop." We build the systems, skills, and habits that produce real, measurable growth.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Let's Work Together</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-gray-300); margin: var(--space-md) auto 0; max-width: 480px;">Whether you're a founder figuring out sales for the first time or a team lead looking to level up your pipeline, I'd love to talk.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary btn--large mt-xl">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
